text: Þis synt þa land gemæro to oswalding tune.
Ærest ælfgyðe mearc on eastan oð teting ford þonne þonan west oþ done þonne þonan oþ eadgife mearce þonne þonan to þæs biscopes mearce to cirringe of cirringe norþ þonan to emecing mere.
And trip hyrst & insnadis into oswalding tune.
And seo mæd æt brunes forda & seo mæd æt beo broce hierþ into oswalding tune.
Þis is Oswalding tunes boc þe Eadmund cing gebocade æþelswiþe on ece yrfe.
